{"type": "article", "id": 6254, "title": "Walkr", "description": null, "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": null, "author": 3603, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/default_images/missing_article.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;padding:0px;color:#737373;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/walkr-galaxy-adventure-in/id834805518?mt=8\" target=\"_blank\">Walkr</a> 是一款多少为你出门走亲戚增加点动力的游戏。办公室的崔同学评价它为“一个裹着计步游戏外衣，实打实的农场收菜模式”的游戏。为了收集游戏中各种可爱的小星球，你除了等待，就是多走走路，积累能量来缩短等待的时间了。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;padding:0px;color:#737373;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604213615Ik9y5DbT8ldL2nhA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.89375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;padding:0px;color:#737373;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"color:#000000;\">在窜门的时候带上手机，每隔一两小时就盘剥一轮你的星球，你会发现其实一天过得也挺快的。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;padding:0px;color:#737373;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"color:#000000;\">更详细的介绍请戳</span><a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/display/articles/5069.html\" style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;color:#0069D6;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">这里</span></a><span style=\"color:#000000;\">。</span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}